text: Dihydrotestosterone acetate, also known as androstanolone acetate or stanolone acetate, as well as 5α-dihydrotestosterone 17β-acetate, is a synthetic androgen and anabolic steroid and a dihydrotestosterone ester that was never marketed. ==See also== * List of androgen esters § Dihydrotestosterone esters ==References== Category:Abandoned drugs Category:Acetate esters Category:Androgens and anabolic steroids Category:Androstanes Category:Dihydrotestosterone esters Category:Prodrugs Category:Testosterone
title: Dihydrotestosterone acetate
